{"_path":"/maps/_ai/llm/embeddings","_dir":"llm","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Embeddings 入门指南","description":"LLM Embeddings 的核心概念、演进历史与实践","original_path":"_ai/llm/embeddings.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"核心概念"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心概念"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embeddings（词向量/嵌入）是将文本转换为数值向量的技术，是 LLM 理解语言的语义基础。当文本进入模型时，首先被转换为高维向量空间中的点，语义关系变为数学关系。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"好的-embedding-有什么特征"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"好的 Embedding 有什么特征？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语义表示"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：语义相近的词在向量空间中距离更近。如 \"cat\" 和 \"dog\" 的向量应比 \"dog\" 和 \"strawberry\" 更相似"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"维度权衡"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：低维度向量（50-300）存储和计算效率高，高维度向量（768-7168）能捕获更复杂关系但易过拟合。GPT-2 最小 768 维，DeepSeek-V3 达 7168 维"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"静态-vs-动态-embeddings"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"静态 vs 动态 Embeddings"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"静态 Embeddings"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：Token 在输入层获得的固定向量，每个 token 有唯一的嵌入向量"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"动态/上下文 Embeddings"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：经过 Transformer 层处理后，融入上下文信息的表示。\"银行\"在\"河岸\"和\"银行抢劫\"中静态 embedding 相同，但动态 embedding 会根据上下文分化"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"技术演进"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"技术演进"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"tf-idf词频-逆文档频率"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TF-IDF（词频-逆文档频率）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基于统计的方法，通过计算词在文档中的重要性生成嵌入："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TF（词频）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：词在文档中出现频率，越高越重要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"IDF（逆文档频率）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：词在所有文档中的稀缺程度，常见词（如\"的\"）权重低"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"局限性"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：词在向量空间中的距离与语义无关，仅反映共现频率。大多数词的 embedding 聚集在同一区域，缺乏区分度。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"word2vec"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Word2Vec"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神经网络驱动的嵌入方法，核心思想是通过上下文预测词（或反之）："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"CBOW"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：根据上下文词预测目标词"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Skip-gram"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：根据目标词预测上下文词"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"网络结构简单：输入层 → 隐藏层（存储 embeddings）→ 输出层。训练完成后丢弃输出层，隐藏层即为词向量。通过 Negative Sampling 优化大规模词汇表的训练效率。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"优势"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：能捕获语义关系，支持向量运算（如 king - man + woman ≈ queen）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"bert"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"BERT"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"首个基于 Transformer 的上下文嵌入模型， encoder-only 架构："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Tokenizer"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：将文本分割为 token 序列"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embedding"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：将 token 转为向量"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Encoder"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：多层自注意力 + 前馈网络，融合上下文"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Task Head"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：任务特定的输出层"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"预训练任务："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Masked Language Modeling"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：预测被遮蔽的词"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Next Sentence Prediction"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：判断两句子是否连续"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"突破"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：同一词在不同上下文中产生不同表示，解决了多义词问题。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"现代-llm-的-embeddings"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"现代 LLM 的 Embeddings"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"LLM 的 embedding 层作为查找表（Look-up Table）工作：给定 token ID，返回对应的嵌入向量。"},{"type":"element","tag":"code","props":{"className":[]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"torch.nn.Embedding"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 本质上是接收索引而非 one-hot 编码的线性层。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embedding 在 LLM 训练中与模型参数一起优化，而非使用预训练的 Word2Vec——这样 embedding 能针对特定任务和数据定制。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"可视化与分析"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"可视化与分析"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"embedding-atlas"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embedding Atlas"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将词汇 embedding 映射到二维/三维空间可视化，语义相近的词会聚集。例如 \"bridge\"、\"bridges\"、\"桥\"、\"橋\" 在空间中距离很近，反映了跨语言的语义相似性。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://apple.github.io/embedding-atlas/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Apple Embedding Atlas"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - Apple 开源的大规模嵌入可视化工具，支持自动聚类、实时搜索、WebGPU 渲染"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"embedding-graph"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Embedding Graph"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"将 embedding 空间建模为图网络：token 为节点，向量相近的 token 之间建立边。可用于分析词汇的语义邻域结构。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"实践工具"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"实践工具"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"TensorFlow Embedding Projector"}]},{"type":"text","value":"："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://projector.tensorflow.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"projector.tensorflow.org"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 交互式 embedding 可视化"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MTEB Leaderboard"}]},{"type":"text","value":"："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":